rows.label: qst702703_msg0001
rows.name:
I need you to defeat the
monster holed up at the bridge
before the Haradd Hills.

rows.label: qst702703_msg0002
rows.name:
If the delivery is late, who
knows how many punches I'll
get from my old man...

rows.label: qst702703_msg0101
rows.name:
You defeated it! As expected
of a Driver... Thank you!

rows.label: qst702703_msg0102
rows.name:
What a joke, "simple manual
labor". This is anything but
simple, you old fool!

rows.label: qst702703_msg0103
rows.name: ...Gotta hurry, or it's punches for me!

rows.label: qst702703_msg0104
rows.name:
Here! It's not much,
but please take it.

rows.label: qst702703_msg0105
rows.name:
My family are gardeners in
the capital. If you're ever
nearby, come say hi!

rows.label: qst702703_msg0106
rows.name:
Right then, the sand... How much
did he say he needed again?

rows.label: qst702703_msg0107
rows.name:
Well, I'll figure it
out when I get there!
